gujarati.context:
Ati pratapī ehe, uddhava jēvā e ānup;
Jñāna guṇa ne lakṣane, thāśe tehe jēvā tadrūp.

To English:

This is extremely powerful, like Uddhav; 
Knowledge and virtues are its characteristics, it will be like that.

Ur vishal bhaal zhalek, shee she ke shyaam che;
Zee-na vakr zage ghana, vaali prood ponde Shriram che.

The Ur is vast and dark, the Sheesh is like that of Shyam; 
The crooked twists are many, the wise Pundit worships Shriram.
